  <name>Witnessd</name>
  <summary>Cryptographic authorship witnessing daemon</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Witnessd provides cryptographic authorship witnessing through kinetic
      proof of provenance. It captures keystroke dynamics and timing patterns
      to create unforgeable evidence of human authorship.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Merkle Mountain Range (MMR) append-only log for tamper-evident storage</li>
      <li>Ed25519 digital signatures for cryptographic proof</li>
      <li>Privacy-preserving keystroke biometrics</li>
      <li>Multi-anchor timestamping (blockchain, Keybase, etc.)</li>
      <li>Forensic analysis toolkit for verification</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

  <launchable type="desktop-id">witnessd.desktop</launchable>

